<section class="relative pb-16 lg:pb-0 bg-hero-gradient overflow-hidden lg:h-[320px] lg:flex lg:items-center">
    {/* Decorative element (Semi-circle and Image) */}
    <div class="absolute inset-0 hidden lg:flex pointer-events-none z-10">
        <div class="container mx-auto w-full flex items-end justify-end">
            <div class="relative w-[35%] h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-end">
                <!-- Semi-circle background -->
                <div class="absolute top-0 w-[400px] h-[200px] bg-ultimate-yellow rounded-b-full right-0 -translate-y-[60px] z-0"></div>
                <!-- Hero Image -->
                <img src="/images/hero_img.png" alt="Kursus Persiapan IELTS" class="absolute z-10 h-[95%] w-auto object-contain object-bottom right-[10%]" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full relative z-20 text-left">
        <div class="container mx-auto py-12 md:py-16 px-4 md:px-6 xl:px-0">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 max-w-2xl px-4 lg:px-0">
                <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-ultimate-yellow text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold mb-6 animate-float uppercase tracking-wider">IELTS Preparation</div>
                <h1 class="font-heading font-semibold text-white text-3xl md:text-[48px] mb-6 leading-tight">Kursus Persiapan IELTS</h1>
                <p class="text-slate-200 text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed font-light">
                    Raih skor impianmu dengan bimbingan intensif dari pengajar ahli. Fokus pada penguasaan materi, strategi pengerjaan soal, dan simulasi tes yang komprehensif.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
